quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  27,56,"Empa karabo ea batho ba habo e bile feela hore; ba re: “Lelekang balateli ba Lota motseng oa lona, hobane Ruri! Ke banna ba labalabelang bohloeki!”"
  27,57,Empa Re ile Ra mo pholosa le lelapa la hae ntle feela le mosali oa hae; Re ile Ra mo behella kathoko hore a tle a be har’a ba saletseng morao
  27,58,Eaba Re ba nesetsa majoe a lengetane. Pula e nyonyehang holima batho ba ileng ba khalengoa
  27,59,"E re: “Lithoriso li be ho Allah, khotso e be ho makhabunyane A Hae ao A a khethileng! Ana ke Allah Ea molemo, kapa ba molemo ke batlatsetsi ba ba manamisang ho Eena"
  27,60,"Ana ha se Eena Ea Molemo Ea hlotseng maholimo le lefats’e le hona ho le romella pula e tsoang marung, eo ka eona Re hlahisang lirapa tsa litholoana tse hlabosang, seo lifate tsa sona li sa kang tsa lengoa ke lona. Ana ho teng `Mopi e mong kathoko ho Allah? Eu, empa batho ba maneha ba tlatsetsi ho Eena"
  27,61,"Kapa, ha se Eena Ea entseng lefats’e hoba lehae le tsepameng, A ba A theha linoka ho lona, le hona ho theha lithaba holim’a lona le hona ho tsepamisa moeli lipakeng tsa maoatle a mabeli? Ana ho teng `Mopi e mong ntle ho Allah? Che bongata ba bona ha bo tsebe letho"
  27,62,"Ana ha se Eena Ea arabelang ea bohlokong nakong eo a bitsang ho Eena, e be U mo imolla bothateng, A etse majalefa a lefats’e? Joale, ana ho teng `Mopi e mong ntle ho Allah? Ruri! ba nahana hanyenyane"
  27,63,"Ana ha se Eena Ea le tataisang har’a lefifi la naha le leoatle, Ea romellang liphefo tse phatlalatsang Mohau oa Hae? Ana o teng `Mopi e mong ntle ho Allah? Ea hloahloeng ke Allah kahofetisisa ho batlatsetsi bohle ba ba manehang ho Eena"
  27,64,"Kapa, Ea hlahisang tlholeho, A boele A e phete hape, Eena Ea le nehang nala ho tsoa leholimong le lefats’eng? Joale, ana ho teng `Mopi e mong ntle ho Allah? E re: “Hlahisang bopaki ba lona haeba le hlile le buoa ‘nete!”"
  27,65,"E re: “Ha ho ope ea ka tsebang ka tse patiloeng tsa maholimo le tsa lefats’e haese Allah; ha ba tsebe letho ka letsatsi leo ba tlang ho tsosoa ka lona"
  27,66,Ana tsebo ea bona e pharaletse hoo ba ka fihlelang bophelo bo-tlang? Ba na le khoao. Ke lifofu.”
  27,67,"Mahana-tumelo ba re: “Eng! Ha re se re fetohile lerole,-rona le bo-ntata rona, – ana re sa tla hlola re tsosoa hape"
  27,68,“Ke `nete re ile ra ts’episoa sena.-rona le bo-ntata rona. Empa tsena tsohle ha se letho haese lits’omo tsa mehleng ea khale.”
  27,69,"E re: “Hahlaulang le lefats’e le tle le bone seo ebileng pheletso ea ba bileng molato!”"
  27,70,"U se ke oa ikutloisa bohloko ka bona, le hona ho touta ka lebaka la merero ea bona"
  27,71,"Ba bile ba re: “Ke neng ts’episo ena e tlang ho phethahala haeba u hlile u buoa ‘nete?”"
  27,72,"E re: “Mohlomong karolo ea seo le ka se potlakelang se haufi le lona.”"
  27,73,"Empa ruriMong`a hau U Khaphatseha mohau ho batho, le hoja bongata ba bona bo hloka teboho"
  27,74,Ruri Mong`a hau o tseba ka botlalo lintho tsohle tseo lipelo tsa bona li li patileng le tsohle tseo ba li pepesang
  27,75,"Ha ho letho le patehileng leholimong le lefats’eng, empa se ngoliloe ka har’a buka e hlakileng"
  27,76,Ruri! Qura›n ena e manolletse bana ba Israele boholo ba lintho tseo ba hohlanang ka tsona
  27,77,Ke Tataiso le Mohau ho ba kholoang
  27,78,"Ruri Mong`a hau o tla ahlola lipakeng tsa bona ho latela Bohlale ba Hae, Eena Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Tsebang-Tsohle"
  27,79,"Kahoo beha ts’epo ea hau ho Allah, hobane u tsepame ‘neteng e hlakileng"
  27,80,Ruri! U ke ke ua etsa hore bafu ba utloe le tsona litholo hore li utloe pitso nakong eo li seng li menotse tlhabela
  27,81,"Kapa hona ho tataisa lifofu ho se hlahlathele. Kantle le ba kholoang lits’enolong tsa Rona, ba inehetse Islam"